title: Course 1 - Week 16 & 17
notes: Do Ujjayi Pranayama (#203) without inhalation retention in Siddhasana.

title: Course 1 - Week 19 to 21
notes:
Ujjayi Pranayama without Kumbhaka or retention
(#203) in Siddhasana (84)

title: Course 1 - Week 22 to 25
notes:
Ujjayi Pranayama without Kumbhaka or retention
(#203) in Siddhasana (84)

title: Course 1 - Week 26 to 30
notes:
Ujjayi
Pranayama with Antar Kumbhaka (inhalation retention) (Section 203) in
Siddhasana (84) or in Virasana (89) or in Padmasana (104).

title: Course 1 - Weekly Practice Day 1
notes: half a minute on right side

title: Course 1 - Weekly Practice Day 1
notes: half a minute on left side

title: Course 1 - Weekly Practice Day 1
notes: Nadi Sodhana Pranayama in Padmasana (104) or in Virasana (89) or in Siddbasana (84) with inhalation retention for 10 minutes

title: Course 1 - Weekly Practice Day 2
notes: Ujjayi Pranayama (Section 203) or Nadi Sodhana Pranayama  (Section 205) for 8 minutes in any comfortable asana

title: Course 1 - Weekly Practice Day 3
notes: Ujjayi Pranayama (Section 203) or Nadi Sodhana Pranayama (Section 205) without Kumbhaka or retention

title: Course 2 - Week 31 to 35
notes: All the Padmasana Cycle can be done at a stretch

title: Course 2 - Week 31 to 35
notes:
Nadi Sodhana Pranayama (Section 205) without inhalation retention for
10 minutes

title: Course 2 - Week 36 to 40
notes: Surya Bhedana Pranayama for 5 minutes with inhalation retenion

title: Course 2 - Week 45 to 50
notes: Stay for 5 minutes then the rest of the Sirsasana variations are done in a stretch

title: Course 2 - Week 55 to 60
notes: Urdhva Dhanurasana II for 12 times in technique II

title: Course 2 - Weekly Practice Day 2
notes: Urdhva Dhanurasana I for 12 times in technique I

title: Course 2 - Weekly Practice Day 3
notes: Urdhva Dhanurasana I for 15 times in technique I

title: Course 2 - Weekly Practice Day 4
notes: Urdhva Dhanurasana I for 12 times staying 20 seconds each time

title: Course 2 - Weekly Practice Day 5
notes: Urdhva Dhanurasana I for 15 to 20 times

title: Course 3 - Week 79 to 84
notes: Sit in Siddhasana (84) or VIrasana (89) or Padmasana (104) or Baddha Konasana (102).

title: Course 3 - Week 109 to 125
notes: Work towards practising this 15 times a day

title: Course 3 - Week 146 to 155
notes:
Pranayama of Ujjayi XIII or Surya Bhedana IV
or Nadi Sodhana IVb with inhalation retention
(Antarkumbhaka).

title: Course 3 - Weekly Practice Day 5
notes: All these balancing asanas at one stretch

title: Course 3 - Weekly Practice Day 6
notes: One minute on each way changing legs

title: Course 3 - Week 276 to 300
notes: Ganda Bherundasana and Viparita Shalabhasana together (580, 581, and 584) in one stretch, then go to Urdhva Dhanurasana (486) to do Tiryang Mukhottanasana (586).

title: Course 3 - Final Practice Day 1
notes: Finish each asana 488-499 with Viparita Chakrasana

title: Course 3 - Final Practice Day 3
notes: Sirsapadasana and Ganda Bherundasana, Viparita Salabhasana, and Tiryang Mukhottanasana all done together

title: Course 3 - Final Practice Day 6
notes: include breath retention and at least 8 times Uddiyana
